{"tid":513770,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為你既2017作一個總結","createTime":"2017-12-30T01:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T16:46:08.000Z","uid":18894,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"4be68a648e8ec54701c55c1d6c4483db631aff89","tid":513770,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"寫低2017發生左咩事 <br />\n放低之後係新一年向前看"},{"pid":"d58414f2d28517820e9504975a645adf121ae438","tid":513770,"uid":18894,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"今年真係一直低潮 <br />\n好多野都失敗<br />\n考政府工失敗<br />\n考車肥佬<br />\n連愛情都唔順利<br />\n<br />\n但今年有唔少既改變<br />\n箍牙 考球證 執左個look<br />\n<br />\n利申 識我既唔好相認<br />\n<br />\n希望大家2018開開心心"},{"pid":"577b645a987dbbc778a86cb857a89717185ead93","tid":513770,"uid":118508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"足球球證?"},{"pid":"9f59abf1486c0dfb6f98ded73899bff9cde71c0c","tid":513770,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"又打多左幾百次飛機<br />\n<br />\n仲係青頭仔"},{"pid":"b5b9158dd62553457fb8979fba62ff104bd9f623","tid":513770,"uid":18894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"577b645a987dbbc778a86cb857a89717185ead93","tid":513770,"uid":118508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"足球球證?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"係呀"},{"pid":"ccc381c6f523cf6b96c275a6846ab067265713c2","tid":513770,"uid":146924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"同自己講一句會過去的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2017真係過得好唔容易"},{"pid":"e063f0fffbc08209668b65546460491c6c515dd7","tid":513770,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc381c6f523cf6b96c275a6846ab067265713c2","tid":513770,"uid":146924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"同自己講一句會過去的<img src