有抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n年中搵番一個斷左成年聯絡嘅女仔<br />\n大家正正常常講野可以曖昧下<br />\n有俾過小小surprise佢<br />\n12月你生日慶祝唔到 所以約你聖誕果期 出黎前一日就360度大轉變<br />\n唔想俾假希望我<br />\n轉變大到我嚇親  自己講錯野令佢完全避開<br />\n其實我好想搵你 好想問你係咪發生左咩大事  你可以同我講架我都係你嘅樹窿黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知你會上呢度   想你睇到但驚你睇到避得仲遠<br />\n<br />\n總結：2017 我屌你咩  我失去嘅野太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992f734b5e05dd698f3b11848267ccd6897af838","tid":513770,"uid":50162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"一塌糊塗"},{"pid":"ce87f0c7bd303c63e96ca55df1b2ed5759433cd1","tid":513770,"uid":20341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e15b636fece5582f1d16f24f166f863430e11ca8","tid":513770,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b455c59889cd1dc0ea7b89212d73365d225a5c","tid":513770,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65fd90023a454fc2abb057ff2c20515b290e73e","tid":513770,"uid":20341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"絲打評我分比7.5/10 我<br />\n而我自問一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都唔夠樓主靚仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"🍇<br />\n一定好靚仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"7.5咁高仲唔靚仔<br />\n我肥毒柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"屌啦 靚仔會冇人陪過聖誕除夕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我人太瘦身型唔好睇呢"},{"pid":"f4f199844963ada7e7f04eb0abb8b39ddd6af62c","tid":513770,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"唔太順利 好煩 好多野要係<br />\n2018年頭面對<br />\n成日話係對我好 幫我<br />\n其實就推個波要我處理<br />\n<br />\n想開開心心 但開心唔落<br />\n仲要俾人話 一開始做錯決定<br />\n令到之後條路難行<br />\n但我想講 無一條路易行<br />\n條條路都煩 咁唔通唔向前？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=